      <title>Dollar General 预测 2024 年销量将因需求稳定而乐观，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/dollar-general-projects-2024-profit-below-estimates-costs-pinch-2024-03-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dollar General周四预测的年销售额将高于华尔街的预期，因为更多受通胀影响的客户会购买更便宜的杂货和必需品，导致其股价在盘前飙升逾6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/dollar-general-projects-2024-profit-below-estimates-costs-pinch-2024-03-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 11:11:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
